4–2582. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Deepfool:+A+simple+andaccurate+method+to+fool+deep+neural+networks&conference=Proceedings+of+the+2016+IEEE+Conference+on+Computer+Vision+and+Pattern+Recognition+(CVPR)&author=Moosavi-Dezfooli,+S.-M.&author=Fawzi,+A.&author=Frossard,+P.&publication_year=2016&pages=2574%E2%80%932582&doi=10.1109/CVPR.2016.282" class='google-scholar' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Google Scholar</a>] [<a href="https://doi.org/10.1109/CVPR.2016.282" class='cross-ref' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>CrossRef</a>]</li><li id='B26-electronics-14-00764' class='html-xx' data-content='26.'>Tang, W.; Li, B.; Tan, S.; Barni, M.; Huang, J. CNN-based adversarial embedding for image steganography. <span class='html-italic'>IEEE Trans. Inf. Forensics Secur.</span> <b>2019</b>, <span class='html-italic'>14</span>, 2074–2087. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=CNN-based+adversarial+embedding+for+image+steganography&author=Tang,+W.&author=Li,+B.&author=Tan,+S.&author=Barni,+M.&author=Huang,+J.&publication_year=2019&journal=IEEE+Trans.+Inf.+Forensics+Secur.&volume=14&pages=2074%E2%80%932087&doi=10.1109/TIFS.2019.2891237" class='google-scholar' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Google Scholar</a>] [<a href="https://doi.org/10.1109/TIFS.2019.2891237" class='cross-ref' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>CrossRef</a>]</li><li id='B27-electronics-14-00764' class='html-xx' data-content='27.'>Yang, J.; Liao, X. ACGIS: Adversarial Cover Generator for Image Steganography with Noise Residuals Features-Preserving. <span class='html-italic'>Signal Process. Image Commun.</span> <b>2023</b>, <span class='html-italic'>113</span>, 116927. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=ACGIS:+Adversarial+Cover+Generator+for+Image+Steganography+with+Noise+Residuals+Features-Preserving&author=Yang,+J.&author=Liao,+X.&publication_year=2023&journal=Signal+Process.+Image+Commun.&volume=113&p