                <h2><a name="cite"></a>Share and Cite</h2>

                <div class="social-media-links" style="text-align: left;">
                    <a href="mailto:?&amp;subject=From%20MDPI%3A%20%22ASIGM%3A%20An%20Innovative%20Adversarial%20Stego%20Image%20Generation%20Method%20for%20Fooling%20Convolutional%20Neural%20Network-Based%20Image%20Steganalysis%20Models&quot;&amp;body=https://www.mdpi.com/3184382%3A%0A%0AASIGM%3A%20An%20Innovative%20Adversarial%20Stego%20Image%20Generation%20Method%20for%20Fooling%20Convolutional%20Neural%20Network-Based%20Image%20Steganalysis%20Models%0A%0AAbstract%3A%20To%20defeat%20AI-based%20steganalysis%20systems%2C%20various%20techniques%20using%20adversarial%20example%20attack%20methods%20have%20been%20reported.%20In%20these%20techniques%2C%20adversarial%20stego%20images%20are%20generated%20using%20adversarial%20attack%20algorithms%20and%20steganography%20embedding%20algorithms%20sequentially%20and%20independently.%20However%2C%20this%20approach%20can%20be%20inefficient%20because%20both%20algorithms%20independently%20insert%20perturbations%20into%20a%20cover%20image%2C%20and%20the%20steganography%20embedding%20algorithm%20could%20significantly%20lower%20the%20undetectability%20or%20indistinguishability%20of%20adversarial%20attacks.%20To%20address%20this%20issue%2C%20we%20propose%20an%20innovative%20adversarial%20stego%20image%20generation%20method%20%28ASIGM%29%20that%20fully%20integrates%20the%20two%20separate%20algorithms%20by%20using%20the%20Jacobian-based%20Saliency%20Map%20Attack%20%28JSMA%29.%20JSMA%2C%20one%20of%20the%20representative%20l0%20norm-based%20adversarial%20example%20attack%20methods%2C%20is%20used%20to%20compute%20a%20set%20of%20pixels%20in%20the%20cover%20image%20that%20increases%20the%20probability%20of%20being%20classified%20as%20the%20non-stego%20class%20by%20the%20steganalysis%20model.%20The%20reason%20for%20this%20calculation%20is%20that%20if%20a%20secret%20message%20is%20inserted%20into%20the%20limited%20set%20of%20pixels%20in%20such%20a%20way%2C%20noise%20is%20only%20required%20for%20message%20embedding%2C%20and[...]" title="Email">
