                    <a href="	                    http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%2F3184382&amp;title=ASIGM%3A%20An%20Innovative%20Adversarial%20Stego%20Image%20Generation%20Method%20for%20Fooling%20Convolutional%20Neural%20Network-Based%20Image%20Steganalysis%20Models%26source%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%26summary%3DTo%20defeat%20AI-based%20steganalysis%20systems%2C%20various%20techniques%20using%20adversarial%20example%20attack%20methods%20have%20been%20reported.%20In%20these%20techniques%2C%20adversarial%20stego%20images%20are%20generated%20using%20adversarial%20attack%20algorithms%20and%20steganography%20embedding%20%5B...%5D" onclick="windowOpen(this.href,600,800); return false" title="LinkedIn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
